      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and filled it with vinegar; dipping it into it, it sucked it up. Some of these sponges had leathern handles to them. (r). ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And put it on a reed; a stalk of hyssop; See Gill on John 19:29, ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "And put it on a reed; a stalk of hyssop; See Gill on ",
            "children": []
          },
